歌迷们正在重新分享特蕾西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 1989 年格莱美原创表演《Fast Car》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-are-re-sharing-tracy-chapmans-original-grammys-performance-of-fast-car-from-1989-3582823?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=粉丝们正在重新分享 1989 年特雷西·查普曼斯原创格莱美快车表演Elizabeth AubreyMon, 05 Feb 2024 21:38:53 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3582823 <p><img width="2000" height="1272" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 出席 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “音乐界真正的宝石”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-are-re-sharing-tracy-chapmans-original-grammys-performance-of-fast-car-from-1989-3582823">粉丝们正在重新分享特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 1989 年格莱美原创表演《Fast Car》，该歌曲</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1272" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 出席 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-800x509.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-696x443.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tracey-Chapman-at-the-2024-Grammys-Photo-by-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Recording-Academy-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>特雷西<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tracy-chapman">·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman)</a>于昨晚（2 月 4 日）出席颁奖典礼后，网上粉丝们不断转发特蕾西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 在 1989 年格莱美颁奖典礼上表演的原创<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">歌曲</a>《Fast Car》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/the-2024-grammys-the-biggest-talking-points-3582470">2024 年格莱美奖：最大的话题</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚，查普曼与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luke-combs">卢克·库姆斯</a>一起登上<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/2024-grammys">2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼</a>的舞台，共同表演了她 1988 年单曲《Fast Car》的一个版本。</p><p>库姆斯去年发行了这首歌的翻唱版，帮助这首歌重新复兴。他的版本已在美国获得双白金认证，并荣获 2023 年乡村音乐协会奖 (CMA) 年度单曲奖和年度歌曲奖。</p><p>这位明星此前已被确认将出席 2024 年格莱美颁奖典礼，颁奖典礼前几天有报道称查普曼将与他一起登台。自 2009 年上一次巡演结束以来，她只在镜头前表演过几次。</p><p>现在，演出结束后，网上的粉丝们开始分享查普曼的原创表演，以及他们对此的看法，如下所示。一位用户称她为“一位令人惊叹的歌手和偶像”，而另一位用户则称她是“音乐界真正的宝石”。</p><p>查看原始性能以及以下一些反应： </p><p><iframe title="特雷西·查普曼 - Fast Car (Live 1989)" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IG79CHK1oFQ?start=4&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">客观地说， <a href="https://twitter.com/taylorswift13?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@taylorswift13</a>诞生那一年的原始格莱美表演： <a href="https://t.co/08UDClCB7D">https://t.co/08UDClCB7D</a></p><p> — 菲奥娜·马塔尔博士<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1faa9.png" alt="🪩" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@FionaMattatall） <a href="https://twitter.com/FionaMattatall/status/1754372238072308207?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 5 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我第一次听到这首歌是在 1989 年的格莱美颁奖典礼上，从那时起我就成了歌迷。特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 依然摇滚，即使已经 35 岁了。音乐界真正的瑰宝<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2764-fe0f-200d-1f525.png" alt="❤️‍🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2764-fe0f-200d-1f525.png" alt="❤️‍🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2764-fe0f-200d-1f525.png" alt="❤️‍🔥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> — @YenChenKL_Busy，检查开启和关闭<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f605.png" alt="😅" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> (@YenChenKL1) <a href="https://twitter.com/YenChenKL1/status/1754495888918303097?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 2 月 5 日</a></p>